Scope of this licence

This MIT licence applies to the *packaging* in this repository — the Nix
expressions, build scripts, CI workflows, and documentation authored here.

It does NOT relicense the chess engines themselves. Each engine's source is
fetched from its own upstream at build time and remains under that upstream's
own licence (GPL-2.0/3.0, AGPL-3.0, MIT, BSD, Zlib, Apache-2.0, etc.). Those
licences, and their obligations, are unaffected by this file. See each
`engines/<name>.nix` for the per-engine licence and `docs/excluded.md` for the
licensing determinations behind what is and isn't included.
